5/22/00
  Attempt to solve GI DCT 1000 problem by modifying the first TP of each
  output pictures to avoid PES header followed by ES header:
  - For each picture, in Splicer, add 1 to the actual TP count
    if it has PES header.
  - In Output, fill PES header to end of TP.
    Added another TP for ES header.  Use AF filling.

  Support the new PPC change which use different SPID for synchronized (ACKs)
  and asynchronized messages (SPLICE_INDICATION, DEBUG_PRINT, MUX_RATE).
  Need to change both dpi and statmux codes.


